casebody.data:
INTERPIPE CONTRACTING, INC., petitioner,
v.
Xavier BECERRA, Attorney General of California, et al. No. 18-1065. Supreme Court of the United States June 24, 2019.

Motion of Associated General Contractors of America for leave to file out of time a brief as amicus curiae denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
